so I'll start by saying
that I'm sorry

24:48.175 --> 24:49.675
and that my hand still hurts.

24:49.710 --> 24:51.210
His face has sharp edges.

24:51.244 --> 24:53.829
Okay, I'm-I'm not...
I'm not mad, I...

24:53.880 --> 24:56.415
Actually, I think I owe
you a debt of gratitude.

24:56.449 --> 24:58.084
Just, um...

24:58.118 --> 25:00.803
you know, I wish that you
would've stayed and...

25:00.837 --> 25:03.723
hung around a little longer.

25:03.757 --> 25:06.759
Next time, I promise.

25:06.793 --> 25:09.061
So, how is college?

25:09.096 --> 25:11.097
It's a dream come true.

25:11.131 --> 25:12.315
Parties with Puck...

25:12.349 --> 25:14.233
Puck? Puck is there?

25:14.267 --> 25:15.484
Yeah, he's here.

25:15.519 --> 25:16.652
Long story, but...

25:16.687 --> 25:17.653
it's amazing.

25:17.688 --> 25:18.821
Every night, we go out,

25:18.855 --> 25:19.989
we-we're meeting new people...

25:20.023 --> 25:21.157
Well, then, that sounds amazing.

25:21.191 --> 25:22.658
I'm... it's really great.

25:22.693 --> 25:24.694
I, uh, actually I just,

25:24.745 --> 25:26.028
I needed to, um,

25:26.079 --> 25:28.080
to ask you something.

25:28.115 --> 25:30.700
Let me guess:
<i>Funny Girl</i> auditions.

25:32.152 --> 25:34.503
I knew you'd remember.

25:34.538 --> 25:36.339
Finn, I can't believe
that this moment is happening,

25:36.373 --> 25:38.507
and I know that
this is a long shot,

25:38.542 --> 25:42.044
