26:06.987 --> 26:10.039
And I know you have it in you.

26:10.073 --> 26:11.540
(sighs)

26:11.575 --> 26:13.209
Wow.

26:13.243 --> 26:14.493
Thank you, that was, uh...

26:14.527 --> 26:17.380
perfect advice.

26:17.414 --> 26:19.715
You'll be great.

26:19.750 --> 26:22.918
Can't wait to come
to a show sometime.

26:22.969 --> 26:24.970
Call me as soon
as it's over, okay?

26:25.005 --> 26:27.807
I will.

26:33.764 --> 26:35.765
