30:07.927 --> 30:10.646
Um, how I wouldn't be
the person I am today,

30:10.697 --> 30:12.031
standing in front of you,

30:12.065 --> 30:13.616
doing what I'm doing

30:13.650 --> 30:16.735
right now if they hadn't
shown me that I could.

30:17.821 --> 30:19.655
If they hadn't believed in me.

30:21.541 --> 30:22.825
Thank you.

30:32.631 --> 30:33.798
